{"tid":1810623,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員蛇足10年無人發現，打卡即走每年46萬袋袋平安！","createTime":"2020-01-04T04:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:33:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fbfdc0378f042f7e4e1553c6a78e528b6ea9d44a","tid":1810623,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"公務員一直是人們眼中「鐵飯碗」，而近日西班牙一名公務員則以身示範如何「打爛飯碗」。他不但年入46萬港幣，每天上班打卡完後便「蛇」出去，直到收工時間又回來打卡，這樣的行為整整持續了10年都沒人發現，直到前年夏天遭人指控後才被當地政府開除。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/20200101_pl_salary1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F20200101_pl_salary1.jpg&h=64a477be&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，Carles Recio 是西班牙一間法院檔案保管所的副所長，他被指控，每天早上7時30分左右上班，但在出勤簿上填寫完時間後就會閃人，接著在下午4時再返回填寫下班時間，Carles Recio 就這樣幹了10年都沒出事。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/20200101_pl_salary.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F20200101_pl_salary.jpg&h=11e28c92&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n一直到前年夏天，同事看不下去才讓事情曝光，Carles Recio 也因此被開除。不過，Carles Recio 喊冤表示，「我常常像奴隸一樣工作，我不在辦公室的時候，常常要處理一堆文書、信件。」Carles Recio 還強調，自己不想待在辦公室，是因為被同事孤立。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/05/1123395-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F1123395-XXL.jpg&h=dd9a6c9c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n西班牙當地法院最後認定，Carles Recio 確實忽視「工作崗位上應盡的職責」，且長期沒執行職務，判他在未來9年內不得在公務機關就職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=662798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D662798&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=df9e4ab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D662798&h=6c7e859b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=662798</a>"},{"pid":"61483ac4f2cb215ce92869381e60bceeefabffb7","tid":1810623,"uid":32577,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上司同同事都唔理佢先好野<br />\n仲要成10年"},{"pid":"2a8b5bda02a146bed0356ccd767dad4c3b06f2f7","tid":1810623,"uid":87684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61483ac4f2cb215ce92869381e60bceeefabffb7","tid":1810623,"uid":32577,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上司同同事都唔理佢先好野<br />\n仲要成10年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"做intern咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191e46b5012140a5fe6d33ec4dc8ed6fd5442978","tid":1810623,"uid":8331,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"香港既公務員都有得揮 之前白粉報都登幾多佢地蛇型既相 果啲一定又係自己友篤灰"},{"pid":"fe27144c7b10213403963ce2af16052f47fb9441","tid":1810623,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"香港都有都唔出奇， 有D 部門成日lunch 後十幾廿分鐘熱線都未開返，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放工前又提早停熱線，唔知D 職員去左邊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.votes.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.votes.hk&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=bc64c0c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.votes.hk</a>"},{"pid":"43683734401a4939c750787a84d2012985f1f9e0","tid":1810623,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61483ac4f2cb215ce92869381e60bceeefabffb7","tid":1810623,"uid":32577,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上司同同事都唔理佢先好野<br />\n仲要成10年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:25:59.000Z","msg":"點解會知有佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630a539ceb16cd67812345a01d5473685719d86f","tid":1810623,"uid":205915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:33:21.000Z","msg":"幾年前嘅新聞又翻炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}